            "body": "I'm not particularly familiar with the internals of Flask, or the Flask way of doing things, so take this with a grain of salt. Personally I'd not cover the last case at all. It doesn't really feel to me like a good option for a CLI. I'd suggest the user write their own command or app instance that uses their custom `SSLContext` instead."
